@Njbear7453 Don’t blame the actors, put the blame where it belongs the producers.

Mr. Craig took a job and read the script he was given. Just as Ford got killed by his son in The Force Awakens, gets cold cocked by a 100 lb female in the last film, I don’t know what he did in the Blade Runner movie, he was an ACTOR. Stop blaming him for his actions because he really doesn’t care.

I will paraphrase the great Michael Caine when he was asked if he had seen the crap fest that was Jaws III. He said that he hadn’t even seen it, but he had seen the home that it bought him and it was fabulous.
